item.title: Collectus
item.description: WHY The motivation of this project is half personal and half academic. Let me explain it. At home my father always collected a lot of things, from the oldest books you can imagine until the most recent new Funko POP, through Swiss Knives or dices among others. Having that variety of objects and a lot of them (too many to be honest) cataloguing that amount of items always had been a challenge for him.
